==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Singlestick
<hw>Sin"gle*stick`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>In
England and Scotland, a cudgel used in fencing or fighting; a
backsword.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The game played with singlesticks, in
which he who first brings blood from his adversary's head is pronounced
victor; backsword; cudgeling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Single-surfaced</ent>⟦br⟧
